{Speech 2}{}{I'm working, buzz off.@@[Pointedly ignores you]@@What do you want@sex@||?@@[Frowns with displeasure and meaningfully racks the bolt]}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{[Leave]}
{Speech 3}{}{Hello.}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{Bye.}
{Speech 3 Answer 4}{}{Got anything for sale?@@Nothing for sale?@@What do you trade in? Or have you got nothing?@@Shall we trade?}
{Speech 3 Answer 5}{}{Got anything for sale?@@Nothing for sale?@@What do you trade in? Or have you got nothing?@@Shall we trade?}
{Speech 4}{}{I'm not some kind of trader. I'm a mercenary. You've got the wrong guy.@@Go on, go on, be on your way. I don't trade.@@You're not in a shop, what trade are you talking about.}
{Speech 5}{}{Of course there is. We've always got something... Only I'm not sure my goods will be to your taste.}
{Speech 5 Answer 6}{}{And what goods? How much do you want?}
{Speech 6}{}{It's no ordinary good. It's a map.}
{Speech 6 Answer 7}{}{What kind of map?}
{Speech 7}{}{The map marks a stash. There was this thing... I hid something, won't be able to retrieve it for a while. Figured I'd sell the map. Interested?}
{Speech 7 Answer 8}{}{Why @sex@|should|should| I believe you? Pay for a scrap of paper?}
{Speech 7 Answer 9}{}{Can you tell me more about what's hidden there?}
{Speech 8}{}{[Shrugs] Don't want to - don't believe me. Your business.}
{Speech 9}{}{It's near one well-known place. From the map you'll figure out where to look right away. What's hidden I won't say, I don't want my partners to overhear. But, you can trust me, I won't overcharge you.\nIn short. The map's for sale, the price is 1000 coins. Will you take it?}
{Speech 9 Answer 10}{}{Just so you know, if you cheat me, I'll dig you out from underground. [Pay 1000 coins]}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit}{}{Go there, I don't know where, fetch the thing, I don't know what? Find another fool.}
{Speech 10}{}{Don't lose the map. On the back is the code for an electronic lock. I rigged it to a crate, just to be safe... Now go.}
{Speech 10 Answer Exit}{}{All right. }
